HEADWORD: Sabretasche
<hw>Sa"bre*tasche`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>sabretache</ets>, G. <ets>s⟦aum⟧beltasche</ets>;
